2.Hotel Menu Design using CSS 
Program Code: 
Menustyle.css (External CSS File) 
.menu-item { 
 display: flex; 
 justify-content: space-between; 
 margin: 12px 0; 
 font-size: 16px; 
} 
.menu-item span:first-child { 
 flex: 1; 
 border-bottom: 1px dotted #aaa; 
 margin-right: 15px; 
} 
.menu-item span:last-child { 
 color: #333; 
 font-weight: bold; 
} 
.menu-image img { 
 width: 100%; 
 height: 100%; 
 object-fit: cover; 
 border-left: 1px solid #c49b3f; 
} 
@media (max-width: 768px) { 
 .menu-section { 
 grid-template-columns: 1fr; 
 } 
 .menu-image img { 
 border-left: none; 
 border-top: 1px solid #c49b3f; 
 } 
}
Hotelmenu.html 
